})
```

Testing this locally, and checking my localStorage on the browser, I'm not seeing any entry.

Btw, `persistSession: false` doesn't delete the local storage on logout - it simple doesn't touch it. So if you've previously visited the site with `persistSession` unset, you might need to manually delete it from local storage first.

